  "A swim team recorded the following 50-meter freestyle times in seconds: 28.5, 30.2, 27.8, 29.1, 31.0, 28.5, 29.7, 30.5. The coach wants to set a benchmark using the mean time. What benchmark time should the coach set, rounded to the nearest tenth?": "",
